3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning image representations and clustering centers jointly. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image clustering and feature learning. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper uses fully convolutional auto-encoders for feature learning.
